Consider the following two graphs: 

Graph A:

_vertices_ {1,2,3,4}

_edges_ {(1,2), (2,3), (3,1), (3,4), (4,1)}

Graph B:

_vertices_ {a,b,c,d}

_edges_ {(a,b), (b,c), (c,a), (c,d), (d,a)}

Determine whether Graph A and Graph B are isomorphic or not. If they are isomorphic, provide an isomorphism between them.
